dc_title_s: Parks and Recreation Winnebago County, Wisconsin, 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent parks and recreational areas for Winnebago County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Winnebago_Parks_Rec_2018.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Winnebago_Parks_2018' and 'Winnebago_Recreation_2018'. [Polygons that represent the boundary or management area for significant facilities in a community. Examples include schools, government facilities, stadiums, casinos, and fire stations. Additional information about each Facility can be organized in to separate tables and related to these locations using the FacilityID key. The feature classification and type schema for the facility sites grew out of work with the Department of Homeland Security's HSIP Program and has evolved to support a diverse set of facilities inventoried for a variety of uses by a local government.]
